Description: Modern GTK4 Video Player with Chromecast Streaming
 Video Chromecast Player is a feature-rich video player with Chromecast
 support, built with GTK4 and GStreamer.
 .
 Features:
  * Modern GTK4/Libadwaita interface
  * Hardware-accelerated video playback (AMD/NVIDIA/Intel)
  * Chromecast streaming support
  * YouTube video playback via URL
  * Playlist management with thumbnails
  * Subtitle support (SRT, ASS, VTT)
  * Multiple audio track selection
  * Video effects and filters
  * A-B loop functionality
  * Chapter navigation
  * Multilingual support (English/German)
 .
 The player supports all common video formats (MP4, MKV, AVI, WebM, MOV, etc.)
 and includes automatic format conversion for Chromecast compatibility.
